Zone B Parking will be charged by hourly rates whereby:
- 1st hour cost RM1.59
- RM1.06 will be charged every subsequent hour. 
- Maximum rate is RM4.77 at Zone B Parking.
*Parking rates are based on per entry basis in Zone B*

Zone B parking will be charged RM1.59 on the first hour and RM1.06 will be charged hourly until you exit the parking which capped at RM4.77 per day.
Please note that Zone B parking is on per entry basis.
